This is the ttylinux build system.  It is a simple build system for a small
family of very small Linux systems for several CPU architectures.  See the
How_To_* files in the ttylinux-build/doc directory.

For official ISO distribution releases see the ttylinux web page:
http://ttylinux.org/

Official ttylinux releases are supported through the mailing list:
http://groups.google.com/group/ttylinux/
